name: Art Deco- Cut Out Ring
description: Sterling silver Cut out ring.  Entirely handmade, cool and comfortable ring.  Art Deco design with modern edge.

name: MINI-MENDED HEART
description:
Now the same coveted "Mended Heart Necklace" is available in MINI! (why do we love mini everything?!!?)
This sterling silver heart charm is cracked down the middle and laced up with gold wire to signify the mending of a broken heart. Set on a sterling silver chain with toggle clasp. Entirely hand made by yours truly :)
This piece contains a different meaning for everyone but no matter the story the message of love and strength always rings true!
A wonderful gift for anyone on your list that has found love or overcome anything life may throw at them. Perhaps its the perfect gift for you! A reminder of our resilience.

name: Corset Ring
description:
Handmade sterling silver corset ring is 'cracked' down the center and laced up with 14K Gold wire.
This beautiful unique design has a high shine and mirror finish 

**Also available with silver wire**

Also pieces are handmade to order.  Please specify ring size.

With the holidays right around the corner be sure to get your orders in early.  Remember it takes 7-10 days for custom orders to be completed.
All jewelry is shipped in a perfectly adorned little box

name: X-Necklace
description:
X marks the spot with this beautiful handmade silver necklace. Two sterling silver swords cross to form a slightly offset "X" secured with a tiny gold  bolt. This slightly asymmetric design lays beautifully on the neck with a dynamic, edgy appeal. Simple yet provocative.
The piece is set on sterling silver chain with silver toggle clasp.
Please specify chain length when ordering. 
If you do not see your size please contact me.

name: Mended Heart Necklace as seen In OSCARS gift lounge!
description:
- The Beauty of the Broken Heart comes from the Strength in the Mended Heart.   

I am pleased to announce that RENEE ANDRIOLE DESIGNS and her  'Mended Heart Necklace'  were featured  in the OSCARS Luxury Gift Lounge this February 2012.  All attendees  received a 'Mended Heart Necklace' in their swag bags.

This lovely piece contains a different significance for everyone but what does ring true is that the piece is about healing and strength.  
The elegant elongated heart is made entirely of sterling silver,  'cracked' down the center, and laced up with gold wire. Sterling silver chain. (16''/ 18'')

All pieces are entirely handmade and unique to each individual.
This heart can be set on a 16" or 18" sterling silver chain.
And can be laced with gold or silver wire.
Please contact me with any questions

name: Double Chain Ring
description:
This sterling silver ring beautifully adorns the hand, you won't be able to take your eyes off of it. Two brushed silver bands sit on different parts of the finger and delicate silver chain drapes between them. One silver band on the top of the finger connected to a smaller silver band on the lower part of the finger by silver chain. Both silver bands have a brushed finish that is complimented by high shine edges and chain.

All pieces are custom made to order so please specify size when applicable.

name: Spike Caltrop Bracelet (Sterling Silver)
description:
When making this bracelet I was inspired by weapon replicas, mostly those of the past. The Caltrop is a weapon used throughout history as early as 331BC. Considered to be the landmines of antiquity, these spikes were used to perimeter enemy areas. The uniqueness of the weapon is that when thrown, the spikes are arranged in a manner that one of them always points upward.
This entire piece sterling silver and completely handmade by me. The spikes themselves are not sharpened, so they will not hurt you when worn, but they do have a pointed shape. Each caltrop was made individually and then woven into a handmade chain. The piece is then finished off with the signature spike toggle clasp.
This piece took countless hours to make by hand and is truely one of a kind.
It is my favorite piece from a collection of weapon replica's that have been shown in art galleries and private exhibits. A true piece of wearable art.

name: Sickle Ring
description:
Amazing sterling silver ring with sickle shape. This ring has three layers of sterling silver fastened together with small brass bolts. The elegant curves and angles of the ring look beautiful on the hand and the luster of the silver catches the eye.

A true piece of wearable art.

name: Criss Cross Necklace
description:
This handmade sterling silver  necklace has a wide 'V' shape and is joined at the bottom with a tiny silver bolt. Three rows of textured silver rope chain drape in the middle . It is set on a sterling silver chain and has a toggle clasp. The chain measures 14" and sits right under the collar bone, framing the beautiful area of the the chest and neck.
Unique piece with an edgy design yet extremely elegant.

name: Silver Spike and Rose Ear Cuff
description:
Who doesn't love spikes and roses???
This sterling silver ear  cuff (no piercing required) hooks on to the the top the earlobe and curves around the ear to keep it in place. It is adorned with a lovely silver rose at the top and the bottom of the cuff  comes to a slight spike.
Long silver chain drapes down and  it is finished with silver beads.
The chains measure 12.5" down from the ear.  I love to wear this piece with my hair up to accentuate to long chains and show off the design.

Please specify what ear you would like to wear it on. The curvature of the piece depends on whether you are wearing it on the right or left ear. 


I am not only interested in aesthetics when making jewelry, but the way it feels on the skin and how the piece moves with the body are all elements I consider when creating a new piece.

All jewelry is handmade to order just for you. Please allow 10 days to be shipped. Please contact me if you need a rush on anything.

All jewelry comes in perfectly adorned little boxes.

name: Spike Bullet Ring
description:
This sterling silver ring has an open design and is made with square shaped silver wire and a small round silver spike at one end.  This ring is edgy, yet understated. Perfect for everyday wear.
It has high shine and a mirror finish. The tiny spike looks like a little bullet shooting out of the ring.

Please include ring size when ordering
Please contact me with ANY questions

With the holidays right around the corner please be sure to get your orders in early.  It will take approximately 7-10 days for custom work to be completed.
All jewelry comes in a perfectly adorned little box

name: Spaced Out Ring
description:
This sterling silver ring has a fun and funky shape extends off the hand in wing type design.
Silver tubing is set at the end of the 'wing' giving this ring a whimsical look.
I love to make jewelry that moves with the wearer. This ring is a statement piece and will have you flying in no time ;)
Sure to get noticed and looks as great as it is fun to wear!

name: Brushed Silver Bolt Ring
description:
This brushed silver band is set slightly askew and connected with a tiny gold bolt. This contemporary design is a little twist on your classic silver band.
The brushed metal and brass bolt gives the piece a slightly antique look.

name: Silver Bangle with Draping Chain
description:
This sterling silver bangle is made to be worn on the forearm. Made from a thick gauge silver wire with six silver chains dangling off of it. The chains alternate between a classic silver round chain and a heavier diamond shaped link. The end of each chain is adorned with a sterling silver bead.
The bracelet moves and flows with you as you dance about your day.... or night ;)
Bracelets are not just for wrists anymore. From Cleopatra to Wonder Woman, women through out history have been wearing bracelets up and down their arm. Transcend time and style with this unique and sexy bracelet.

All jewelry is custom made to order.
Please specify and special requests and contact me with ANY questions

name: Leather and Silver Hand Bracelet with Ring
description:
This light delicate bracelet drapes over your hand and connects to a simple sterling silver band ring.  I used a darker weathered forest green leather for the bracelet and sterling silver chain.  The leather bracelet has two different draping silver chains and finished with a sterling silver toggle clasp. 
The combination of leather and silver is striking in this piece, yet it remains very light and feminine.
Each piece entirely handmade and custom to you, no two are alike.  
  
Please specify ring size when ordering.

name: Broken Heart Necklace
description:
****So maybe you have a broken heart....maybe you are a heartbreaker, or maybe, like me, you just have a little bit of a darker look on love ****
Whatever the reason this sterling silver broken heart has a little bit of unasumming lustre. Can be set on a 16" or 18" sterling silver chain.
Perfect for everyday wear and it's small size makes it great to layer with other necklaces.

name: Big Ol' Mended Heart
description:
By popular demand my classic "Mended Heart" takes on a new look. This big ol' heart is cracked down the middle and stitched up with a trio of silver, gold, and black wire.
Everything about this piece makes it pop!  It sits perfectly on the chest and has a  high shine silver finish.
 The statement piece measures approximately 2'' across and 3 1/2'' long. I love the elongated shape and the curvature of the heart.  It's feminine and fun
  Every piece is handmade to order for you and no two are alike.

There is also two chain options with this piece (see last photo)
1. White and Gold
2. Gold, Silver, and Black


Pricing of this necklace is for base metal (nickle). Please contact me for pricing of piece in sterling silver.

The beauty of the broken heart comes from the strength on the mended heart.

name: Knife Ring
description:
This bold, avant garde piece comes from my collection of weapon replica's. This statement piece has a blade shape and has 3 layers of sterling silver connected with tiny brass bolts. A true piece of wearable art.

Also offered with a long blade, please see "Knife Ring (Long Blade)" in my shop for pictures.

name: Bolted Cut Out Ring
description:
This cut out ring has two layers of sterling silver attached with small brass bolts.  The cut out design fits comfortably with the shape of the fingers and the brass and silver give the piece a nice contrast.  
Inspired by my knife  ring, this piece has many of the same elements but for those that want something edgy more for everyday wear. 

Each piece is custom made, please specify ring size with order.
Please contact me with ANY questions!

name: Sterling Silver Pinky Ring with Rough Diamond
description:
This textured sterling silver pinky ring has two silver chains dangling off of it. At the end of one chain is a rough black diamond bead and the other chain is adorned with a sterling silver triangle bead. A rough diamond is a diamond that has not been cut.
You'll be talking more with your hands just to watch the delicate chain bounce around and move with you!


All pieces are handmade to order.
Please specify ring size when ordering.
Please contact me with ANY questions 

With the holidays right around the corner please be sure to get your orders in early!
All jewelry comes in perfectly adorned little boxes.

name: Silver ChainMaille Ring
description:
Made entirely of sterling silver. Two silver bands are connected with intricate hand- woven Chainmaille pattern. One band fits the top of your finger the smaller band fits on the lower part of your finger. This complex pattern looks like beautiful metal lace on your finger, it has a slight give so you can bend your finger without any discomfort.
I love the look of chainmaille, but we rarely see it in rings, this is a way to merge two of my favorite looks.
Not just a piece of jewelry.....wearable art

All orders are custom made
Please specify ring size when ordering
Please convo me with ANY questions.

With the holidays right around the corner please get your orders in early :) Remember it take about 7-10 days for custom orders to be shipped.
All items will come in perfectly adorned little boxes
If you need something rushed, let me know and we will work it out.

name: Mesh & Chain Ring
description:
This unique ring looks and feels great while dancing around on the hand. The sterling silver band is wrapped with fine silver mesh. I have attached a light silver chain that dangles on the finger and moves with you.
Delicate style with a hint of drama

name: Silver Asymetric Ring
description:
This asymmetric cut out ring has two layers of sterling silver stacked and connected with tiny silver and brass bolts.
I gave the flat silver a more 3-dimensional look by slightly varying each piece in size.

In this universe, when things are symmetric life stands still. It is when things are slightly asymmetrical amazing things occur.

name: Ball & Chain Necklace
description:
The ol' ball and chain never looked so hot!
This bold piece is entirely handmade.  Hand forged silver bead has individual spikes around it with gold fill wire wrapping. The chain is also handmade, each sterling silver link done one at a time and wrapped with gold filled wire.   Y shape looks beautiful on the neck and adjustable clasp allows you to set it on the perfect position.  Edgy, unique, and beautiful. 
A true piece of art.

name: Silver Chain Maille Bracelet
description:
This intricately woven chain maille bracelet is all handmade and finished with my signature spike toggle clasp.
Each ring woven by me, by hand. 
Made entirely of silver this piece has amazing weight and feels great on the skin and wrist. 

Not only do my pieces have to be aesthetically pleasing, but the way it feels on the skin and how the piece interacts with the wearer are all elements I consider when creating a new piece.

name: Black Lace Rings (3)
description:
Lingerie for your fingers!
This listing is for 3 hand sewn, black lace rings. An easy way to add a little something extra to whatever you are wearing. Sexy and sweet.
Mix and match, wear one, two, or ten! Comfortable and looks great worn alone mixed with other rings and jewelry.

....put a little spice in your sugar ;)

These rings come in a set of 3 (see photo) You will receive two wide bands and one thin band.

FYI- The rings are lace and like any fabric have a slight stretch to them.  I recommend fitting it tightly around your finger so they don't fall off.  Sizing is approximate. Refer to the sizing guide below.

Size 5- x-small
Size6-small
Size 7- Medium
Size 8- Large
Size 9- X-Large

If you have any questions about size please contact me.

Rings are also sold individually $8 each

name: Stitched Up Ring
description:
This sterling silver band measures about 1/2" wide. It is expertly stitched all the way around with fine silver wire.
This design gives a great variation to a classic band. The ring has an elegant, high shine finish while the lacing gives it that little extra edge.
Inspired by my popular Corset Ring.

*Gold lacing also available*

name: Byzantine Lace Chain Maille Bracelet
description:
This elaborately woven chainmaille bracelet is sterling silver and completely hand made. That's right, I wove together each and every one of these small silver rings to create this intricate design. The double byzantine lace pattern is accented with a sterling silver and hematite beaded chain that drapes slightly over the wrist.Very unique, like having two bracelets in one! Finished with my signature spike toggle clasp, because I have to give a little bit of edge to everything ;)
This bracelet is made with a lot of silver and has great weight and feels good on.

I love the way the metal feels on the skin and how things drape on the body, all of my pieces are designed to with these elements in mind.

name: Spike Ring
description:
This Sterling silver spike ring with gold wire wrapping is sure to make a statement. The long silver spike resembles a nail ring  and  creates a very interesting angle. It lays beautifully across the hand.  (see photo on model)
Edgy and elegant....a true piece of art.

I am not only interested in aesthetics when making jewelry, but the way it feels on the skin and how the piece moves with the body are all elements I consider when creating a new piece.

All jewelry is handmade to order just for you. Please allow 10 days to be shipped. Please contact me if you need a rush on anything.

All jewelry comes in perfectly adorned little boxes.

name: Knife Ring(Long Blade)
description:
This ring is Inspired by my collection of weapon replica's and definitely makes a statement. The long sterling silver blade is best worn on your pointer finger to allow the blade to run across your hand and other fingers. The base of the blade is layered with 3 pieces of sterling silver and connected with small brass bolts.
Does come with warning and instructions ;)
Wearable Art

name: Draping Chain Silver Necklace
description:
This necklace is made of sterling silver and adorned with sterling silver chain. The chain is threaded through and wrapped around the silver piece.
The silver has a high shine finish and the chain dangles delicately. This edgy design has a fine finish and feminine accent to the neck and chest.

16" sterling silver chain and silver lobster clasp

name: Multi-Chain Silver and Copper Necklace
description:
This necklace is framed with two copper pieces and six strands of silver chain in between. I've used three different styles of chains. Different shapes and thickness make this eclectic design different and fun. The copper and silver contrast in a wonderful way and both have high shine finish to them.
The necklace drapes right below the collar bone and sits on the breast plate area of the chest. The edgy design beautifully accents this lovely, feminine area of the body.
It has an 18" silver chain and sterling silver lobster clasp.

name: Leather and Silver Wrap Bracelet
description: This long leather bracelet is about 1/2" wide and has dark forest green color accented with fine silver mesh. It is a wrap bracelet and wraps around the wrist 3 times. It is completed with my signature sterling silver spike toggle clasp.
